1
00:00:07,841 --> 00:00:11,595
MIKADO: I still don't get it,
but I guess I sort of do.

2
00:00:11,595 --> 00:00:13,931
Something
that seemed life‐changing,

3
00:00:13,931 --> 00:00:15,682
but nothing changed at all.

4
00:00:15,682 --> 00:00:17,309
It was really weird,

5
00:00:17,309 --> 00:00:20,479
but the kind of weird
that could happen to anyone.

6
00:00:20,479 --> 00:00:22,147
Half a year's gone by
since then.

7
00:00:22,147 --> 00:00:24,399
[Cóiste‐Bodhar neighs]

8
00:00:24,399 --> 00:00:26,902
[police siren wailing]

9
00:00:26,902 --> 00:00:29,947
<i>["Headhunt" by Okamoto's]</i>

10
00:00:29,947 --> 00:00:33,033
<i>[man singing in Japanese]</i>

11
00:00:33,033 --> 00:00:40,040
<i>♪ ♪</i>

12
00:01:20,581 --> 00:01:23,292
MIKADO: A world that I'd only
seen in manga and online

13
00:01:23,292 --> 00:01:24,835
is right here in front of me.

14
00:01:24,835 --> 00:01:26,295
‐ You're so lucky!

15
00:01:26,295 --> 00:01:27,337
Don't just stand there.
Come on!

16
00:01:27,337 --> 00:01:29,172
You want to see an urban legend?

17
00:01:29,172 --> 00:01:31,049
‐ Don't jack with the cops,
monster.

18
00:01:31,049 --> 00:01:34,678
‐ Huh? Whoa. What's with
the drastic outfit change?

19
00:01:34,678 --> 00:01:37,055
‐ Masaomi, wake up!
‐ Masaomi!

20
00:01:37,055 --> 00:01:39,391
‐ She and I
have this mutual friend,

21
00:01:39,391 --> 00:01:42,060
and this guy who...

22
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:49,109
<i>♪ ♪</i>

23
00:02:20,766 --> 00:02:23,310
‐ Carmilla Saizou is definitely
a force to be reckoned with.

24
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:24,603
The role is‐‐

25
